data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This adorable house on an oversized lot is a must-see! No flood insurance required! The roof is only 3 years old, new A/c and water heater were installed in 2022 and the septic tank is only 5 years old. Originally a 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with a garage. The garage has been used as a Den/storage room, but it can easily be converted back to a garage if desired! The kitchen comes with a brand new refrigerator, the washer and dryer are also new. The property is all fenced around, great for dogs to run around freely. Enjoy the outdoors of this home, while floating in the pool or sitting in your large covered and screened-in lanai! The property is used as a short term vacation rental. It's conveniently located and just minutes away from Warm Mineral Springs, all the great shops, dining, and entertainment North Port has to offer! It is a short drive to Blue Ridge Park where you can enjoy some fishing, kayaking, or get-togethers in the pavilion. Furnishings optional.
